metadata.name: Chandni
metadata.description:
Chand/Chandni translates to 'moon' in Hindi. 

--

This is a 1/1 piece created by Saphera Peters, to be airdropped to 1 of 55 owners of her free edition 'On Top', which she distributed in New York City during NFT NYC 2022.  'On Top'  commemorates NFT NYC 2022 and celebrates women taking over Web3. More here: https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0xa9a4ad5e3ba6cc09a5a6b22d2bd918b74dc4512d/1
